Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.40,0:03:58.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,凯撒
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.82,0:04:00.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,它们在靠近
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.86,0:04:04.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,科巴
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.80,0:04:26.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在动手吗  父亲
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.20,0:05:32.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,儿子  别动
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.74,0:06:52.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢  科巴
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.85,0:07:16.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,儿子  要三思而后行
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.25,0:08:23.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别不开心了  蓝瞳
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.71,0:08:29.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,受伤能让你变得更强
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.73,0:10:49.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,过来看看你的弟弟
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.87,0:11:07.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,又一个儿子
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.79,0:11:15.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不禁感叹我们已经走多久了  莫里斯
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.97,0:11:22.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,貌似很久了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.52,0:11:29.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还会想他们吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.02,0:11:31.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,人类吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.52,0:11:36.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有时候会
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.07,0:11:41.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我没有像你那样了解过他们
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.95,0:11:46.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我只看到他们坏的一面
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.08,0:11:51.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好的  坏的  现在都不重要了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.75,0:11:54.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,人类自己毁灭了自己
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.88,0:11:57.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,咱们也会打架啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.63,0:12:00.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但咱们是一家人
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.10,0:12:10.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真想知道他们是不是真的都不在了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.77,0:12:13.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,都过了10个冬天了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.48,0:12:17.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,上两个冬天就不见他们的踪迹了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.19,0:12:20.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他们肯定都不在了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.02,0:12:54.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,蓝瞳  换我就不会被那熊伤到  我多快啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.31,0:12:57.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,闭嘴  嘘
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.45,0:13:09.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,天啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.12,0:13:11.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没事的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.55,0:13:25.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没事的  没事的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.72,0:13:26.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别动
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.73,0:13:42.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别动
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.90,0:13:44.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,帮忙
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.82,0:13:46.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快来帮忙
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.49,0:13:47.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不许动
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.91,0:13:52.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在这里
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.41,0:13:57.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我打中他了  我打中他了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.03,0:14:31.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他们打中了灰灰  他们打了我儿子
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.78,0:14:35.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,火箭  先等等
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.08,0:14:43.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们无意伤害你们
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.25,0:14:47.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他们可是猩猩  怎么会听懂你说什么
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.38,0:14:50.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你觉得他们只是普通猩猩吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.82,0:15:04.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,爸爸
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.82,0:15:05.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,马尔科姆  你干什么
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.82,0:15:07.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-爸爸  -马尔科姆
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.24,0:15:08.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没事
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.66,0:15:15.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把枪放下
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.49,0:15:17.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-说什么呢  -放下
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.92,0:15:28.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,滚
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.13,0:15:31.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,天啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.26,0:15:32.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,天啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.85,0:15:37.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好的  我们马上走
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.52,0:15:38.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,滚
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.02,0:15:40.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-慢点  -快走  走
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.86,0:15:46.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的包
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.28,0:15:47.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快走
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.96,0:16:09.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,科巴
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.09,0:16:12.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,跟着他们
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.10,0:16:59.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,找到了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.18,0:17:01.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们得谈谈
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.02,0:17:04.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了  什么事
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.77,0:17:08.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,水坝几乎是完好的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.27,0:17:10.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,估计一周内就能开始为我们提供能源
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.69,0:17:12.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但有个问题  上车再说
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.37,0:17:25.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我打中他了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.17,0:17:27.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我很害怕  不知道该怎么做
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.71,0:17:30.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,天啊  那里有多少只
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.88,0:17:32.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很多  大概80只
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.13,0:17:33.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-至少80只  -好了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.47,0:17:37.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你都没听到他说什么  他们会说话
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.39,0:17:38.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这不可能
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.97,0:17:40.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我跟你说  德雷福斯
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.21,0:17:40.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他们确实会说话  非常惊人
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.01,0:17:43.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,惊人  他们是会说话的猩猩
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.89,0:17:46.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-还他妈带着长矛  -得了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.06,0:17:49.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不知道你认为自己看见或听到了什么
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.57,0:17:52.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但你得给我安静下来  好吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.86,0:17:55.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,病毒方面呢  埃莉  有任何进展吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.99,0:17:57.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们是因为基因免疫
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.33,0:17:59.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不然早就死了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.32,0:18:00.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这你可不能确定
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.70,0:18:02.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她是疾控中心的  她怎么不确定
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.16,0:18:03.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们怎么办
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.16,0:18:04.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.16,0:18:06.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们需要那里的能源
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.04,0:18:09.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他本可以杀死我们  但他没有
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.17,0:18:11.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也许他故意留我们小命  好跟踪我们
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.88,0:18:14.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,找到我们所在  再一举杀光
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.01,0:18:16.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,"他"是指谁
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.38,0:18:18.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这就是我们想告诉你的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.18,0:18:19.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你绝对前所未见
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.35,0:18:21.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他们的首领
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.47,0:18:23.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,绝对非同寻常
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.89,0:18:24.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.31,0:18:27.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-你是这么想的吗  -这是我们看到的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.19,0:18:28.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没错  我们都看到的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.52,0:18:30.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,回去不能再提及此事  懂吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.98,0:18:32.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在没想出办法前一句话也不能提
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.90,0:18:35.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-开什么玩笑  -我不是在开玩笑
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.74,0:18:38.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不想制造恐慌
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.38,0:18:59.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么样  伙计  你还好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.72,0:19:01.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-我的包掉了  -我知道
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.72,0:19:03.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-你的写生本也在里边吗  -没了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.01,0:19:05.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,卡弗刚跟我说
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.25,0:19:07.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不能跟任何人提起那里发生了什么
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.27,0:19:08.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,暂时先别说
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.30,0:19:37.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们必须现在就打过去
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.26,0:19:40.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,以防他们先动手
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.88,0:19:42.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们不知道他们有多少人
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.22,0:19:45.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有多少枪
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.43,0:19:49.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也不知道他们来这里干什么
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.53,0:19:59.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他们开枪打了你儿子  火箭
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.90,0:20:01.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,难道你不想报仇吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.53,0:20:05.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我听凯撒的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.37,0:20:08.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,科巴说得没错
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.62,0:20:12.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他们差点杀了你  灰灰
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.75,0:20:19.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.39,0:20:26.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果挑起战争
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.01,0:20:30.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们可能会失去这些年来建立的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.56,0:20:34.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,家园
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.15,0:20:38.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,家人
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.99,0:20:48.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,未来
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.21,0:20:58.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明早之前我会作出决定
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.81,0:21:10.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,凯撒
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.31,0:21:20.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,多年来我一直被人类囚禁在实验室
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.82,0:21:22.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他们拿我开刀
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.49,0:21:23.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不断地折磨我
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.91,0:21:27.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是你救了我
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.91,0:21:32.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我可以为你做任何事
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.08,0:21:36.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但我们必须展示实力
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.42,0:21:41.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们会的  科巴
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.21,0:22:26.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,借过  借过
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.45,0:22:50.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这他妈可远不只80啊
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.35,0:23:20.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,马尔科姆
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.34,0:23:52.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,猿族
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.56,0:23:58.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不想要战争
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.35,0:24:02.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但若有必要
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.69,0:24:06.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们定将战斗
Dialogue: 0,0:24:38.56,0:24:41.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,猿族的家
Dialogue: 0,0:24:43.06,0:24:47.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,人类的家
Dialogue: 0,0:24:52.11,0:24:55.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要再过来
Dialogue: 0,0:25:34.99,0:25:36.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,各位
Dialogue: 0,0:25:37.82,0:25:41.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,各位  你们得冷静
Dialogue: 0,0:25:47.84,0:25:49.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,各位
Dialogue: 0,0:25:50.46,0:25:52.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所有人
Dialogue: 0,0:25:52.63,0:25:56.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请冷静  我们都是免疫的
Dialogue: 0,0:25:56.47,0:26:00.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们都免疫  不然也不会站在这里
Dialogue: 0,0:26:01.01,0:26:02.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他们怎么找到这的
Dialogue: 0,0:26:03.98,0:26:05.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是我们先找到他们的
Dialogue: 0,0:26:05.10,0:26:06.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你知道他们在哪里
Dialogue: 0,0:26:06.17,0:26:07.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,万一他们回来怎么办
Dialogue: 0,0:26:09.61,0:26:12.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要是他们回来
Dialogue: 0,0:26:12.44,0:26:15.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他们一定会后悔
Dialogue: 0,0:26:16.15,0:26:18.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,尽管现在这座城市的人口不复当年
Dialogue: 0,0:26:18.78,0:26:21.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但它还拥有火力
Dialogue: 0,0:26:22.33,0:26:24.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,身后那批武器弹药
Dialogue: 0,0:26:24.45,0:26:27.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,联邦应急管理局的  国民警卫队的
Dialogue: 0,0:26:27.60,0:26:29.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在都归我们了
Dialogue: 0,0:26:29.21,0:26:31.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,听着
Dialogue: 0,0:26:32.63,0:26:35.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道你们为什么害怕
Dialogue: 0,0:26:35.84,0:26:39.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,相信我  我也害怕
Dialogue: 0,0:26:40.05,0:26:43.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但我知道自己身上背负着你们的信任
Dialogue: 0,0:26:43.93,0:26:46.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们一起闯过鬼门关
Dialogue: 0,0:26:48.35,0:26:52.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们也都知道现在我们面临着什么
Dialogue: 0,0:26:55.28,0:26:58.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,燃料快用完了
Dialogue: 0,0:26:58.91,0:27:01.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这意味着提供不了电力
Dialogue: 0,0:27:01.53,0:27:05.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,意味着我们要过回以前的苦日子
Dialogue: 0,0:27:05.20,0:27:09.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而那边的水坝就是解决方案
Dialogue: 0,0:27:10.54,0:27:13.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只是我们没想到他们也在那边
Dialogue: 0,0:27:13.46,0:27:14.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那现在该怎么办
Dialogue: 0,0:27:14.55,0:27:16.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:27:16.88,0:27:19.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们会想别的办法
Dialogue: 0,0:27:21.26,0:27:23.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为那里的电力
Dialogue: 0,0:27:23.72,0:27:25.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不仅仅能使灯泡发光
Dialogue: 0,0:27:25.72,0:27:28.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还能为我们提供工具
Dialogue: 0,0:27:28.27,0:27:30.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,与外面的世界重新取得联系
Dialogue: 0,0:27:30.77,0:27:33.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,找到外面的同伴
Dialogue: 0,0:27:33.82,0:27:38.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样我们就能开始重建
Dialogue: 0,0:27:39.66,0:27:41.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,并且再造
Dialogue: 0,0:27:44.41,0:27:47.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们失去的世界
Dialogue: 0,0:27:51.25,0:27:53.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,讲得不错
Dialogue: 0,0:27:55.92,0:27:58.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但根本就没有可替代的能源
Dialogue: 0,0:27:59.93,0:28:02.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,水坝是我们的唯一选择
Dialogue: 0,0:28:07.68,0:28:10.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那只能跟他们拼了
Dialogue: 0,0:28:14.31,0:28:16.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还有两周燃料就用完了
Dialogue: 0,0:28:16.48,0:28:17.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,最多能撑三周
Dialogue: 0,0:28:17.69,0:28:18.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道
Dialogue: 0,0:28:18.94,0:28:21.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,燃料一旦用完
Dialogue: 0,0:28:21.28,0:28:23.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我就不能再拿着个扩音器上去
Dialogue: 0,0:28:24.37,0:28:26.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,指望他们平静下来了
Dialogue: 0,0:28:26.87,0:28:30.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们需要电力让无线电发射机重新运作
Dialogue: 0,0:28:30.96,0:28:34.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是与外界取得联系的唯一办法
Dialogue: 0,0:28:34.63,0:28:36.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们得找到其他幸存者
Dialogue: 0,0:28:36.67,0:28:39.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊  幸存者不多了
Dialogue: 0,0:28:40.55,0:28:42.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不能再有人牺牲了
Dialogue: 0,0:28:42.63,0:28:45.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是我们找到了这个地方
Dialogue: 0,0:28:45.80,0:28:47.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-我跟你  -我知道
Dialogue: 0,0:28:48.18,0:28:51.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,靠能源才能让我们回到从前的日子
Dialogue: 0,0:28:52.56,0:28:55.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要是我们不团结  也许就活不下来了
Dialogue: 0,0:28:55.31,0:28:57.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我失去了一切
Dialogue: 0,0:28:58.86,0:29:02.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一想到会再失去身边仅有的...
Dialogue: 0,0:29:05.66,0:29:07.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想回到那里去
Dialogue: 0,0:29:09.16,0:29:11.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,听我说  给我三天时间
Dialogue: 0,0:29:12.04,0:29:13.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,让我跟他谈
Dialogue: 0,0:29:13.53,0:29:14.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,行不通的话  再按你说的做
Dialogue: 0,0:29:14.83,0:29:16.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,万一适得其反  万一他暴怒了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:29:16.67,0:29:20.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你怎么知道他能明白你
Dialogue: 0,0:29:24.01,0:29:26.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他不仅仅是只黑猩猩
Dialogue: 0,0:29:28.35,0:29:30.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我要带些人到尖兵堡
Dialogue: 0,0:29:31.02,0:29:32.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,去军械库找找看
Dialogue: 0,0:29:33.56,0:29:35.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看哪些还能用的
Dialogue: 0,0:29:37.02,0:29:38.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,三天
Dialogue: 0,0:29:38.44,0:29:39.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要是你三天还没回来
Dialogue: 0,0:29:39.86,0:29:40.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们就冲上去
Dialogue: 0,0:29:40.99,0:29:43.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把他们杀到一只不剩
Dialogue: 0,0:29:59.50,0:30:02.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,卡弗正在备车
Dialogue: 0,0:30:02.17,0:30:04.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他跟福斯特还有肯普马上就到
Dialogue: 0,0:30:05.63,0:30:07.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的要带上卡弗吗
Dialogue: 0,0:30:07.35,0:30:08.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他可开枪打了他们
Dialogue: 0,0:30:08.68,0:30:10.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也没办法
Dialogue: 0,0:30:10.10,0:30:12.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他在水利部门工作过
Dialogue: 0,0:30:12.35,0:30:14.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只有他知道怎么让水坝运作起来
Dialogue: 0,0:30:16.56,0:30:18.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,马尔科姆
Dialogue: 0,0:30:18.06,0:30:21.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你去了打算怎么做  打算说什么
Dialogue: 0,0:30:23.53,0:30:25.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我会跟他说实话
Dialogue: 0,0:30:26.45,0:30:28.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,希望赶上他心情好
Dialogue: 0,0:30:34.00,0:30:36.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你一定觉得我疯了
Dialogue: 0,0:30:37.12,0:30:38.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是担心
Dialogue: 0,0:30:39.63,0:30:41.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊  我也是
Dialogue: 0,0:30:42.80,0:30:45.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我仔细想了一遍
Dialogue: 0,0:30:46.51,0:30:49.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要是我连试都不试
Dialogue: 0,0:30:50.89,0:30:52.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那战争就真的无法避免了
Dialogue: 0,0:31:15.41,0:31:16.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把我也带上
Dialogue: 0,0:31:16.50,0:31:18.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有人受伤怎么办  我可以帮忙
Dialogue: 0,0:31:22.04,0:31:24.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我爱你
Dialogue: 0,0:31:25.71,0:31:27.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但我需要你留在这里
Dialogue: 0,0:31:28.63,0:31:31.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不想留下亚历山大一个人
Dialogue: 0,0:31:31.09,0:31:33.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也去
Dialogue: 0,0:31:36.98,0:31:38.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,儿子  那里不安全
Dialogue: 0,0:31:39.69,0:31:41.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,待在你身边总比在这里安全
Dialogue: 0,0:31:42.61,0:31:44.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也去
Dialogue: 0,0:31:44.53,0:31:45.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,求你了
Dialogue: 0,0:32:13.60,0:32:16.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,任何人都不许离开这辆车
Dialogue: 0,0:32:16.81,0:32:18.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,任何人
Dialogue: 0,0:32:18.85,0:32:20.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要是我两个小时还没回来
Dialogue: 0,0:32:20.78,0:32:22.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你就带他们回城
Dialogue: 0,0:32:23.11,0:32:25.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不会有事的
Dialogue: 0,0:35:27.29,0:35:30.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拜托  拜托
Dialogue: 0,0:35:33.59,0:35:35.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请别杀我
Dialogue: 0,0:35:35.80,0:35:38.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,先听我说
Dialogue: 0,0:35:39.68,0:35:41.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道
Dialogue: 0,0:35:42.93,0:35:46.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,"不要再回来"  我知道
Dialogue: 0,0:35:46.56,0:35:48.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我来这里是因为...
Dialogue: 0,0:35:48.48,0:35:50.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好吧  好吧  好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:35:54.02,0:35:57.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好  好  好
Dialogue: 0,0:35:58.61,0:36:01.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我得带你去一个地方
Dialogue: 0,0:36:01.57,0:36:02.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,离这不远
Dialogue: 0,0:36:02.82,0:36:04.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,人类在撒谎
Dialogue: 0,0:36:04.49,0:36:06.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不  不
Dialogue: 0,0:36:08.96,0:36:11.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不  不  不  我发誓
Dialogue: 0,0:36:13.59,0:36:17.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,去了你就明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:36:17.09,0:36:18.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拜托了
Dialogue: 0,0:36:38.69,0:36:41.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,带路
Dialogue: 0,0:37:04.68,0:37:08.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这就是人类所谓的"小型水电站"
Dialogue: 0,0:37:08.56,0:37:11.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,本来是为这里以北的区域供电的
Dialogue: 0,0:37:11.48,0:37:14.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们在试着把线路改装向城市供电
Dialogue: 0,0:37:14.81,0:37:16.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,城里核电站的能源
Dialogue: 0,0:37:16.54,0:37:17.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,几年前就告竭了
Dialogue: 0,0:37:17.57,0:37:20.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这些年一直靠柴油发电机和气化炉度日
Dialogue: 0,0:37:20.15,0:37:23.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但要是能让这个水坝重新发电
Dialogue: 0,0:37:23.07,0:37:27.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就可以将有限的化石能源贮存起来
Dialogue: 0,0:37:34.50,0:37:37.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你能明白我的意思吗
Dialogue: 0,0:37:38.55,0:37:41.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,灯光
Dialogue: 0,0:37:41.59,0:37:43.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:37:44.43,0:37:45.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,灯光
Dialogue: 0,0:37:46.85,0:37:48.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是你的家园
Dialogue: 0,0:37:48.56,0:37:51.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我从没想过将它夺走  真的
Dialogue: 0,0:37:51.39,0:37:56.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但如果你允许我们在这里施工
Dialogue: 0,0:37:56.15,0:37:58.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你还带了别人
Dialogue: 0,0:38:02.36,0:38:03.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就几个人
Dialogue: 0,0:38:04.70,0:38:06.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不会造成任何威胁
Dialogue: 0,0:38:06.70,0:38:08.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不然的话
Dialogue: 0,0:38:08.87,0:38:11.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你随时可以杀了我
Dialogue: 0,0:38:36.40,0:38:38.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:38:39.94,0:38:43.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等等  别慌  别慌
Dialogue: 0,0:38:55.16,0:38:56.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们得把枪给他们
Dialogue: 0,0:38:58.75,0:39:00.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就这一个条件
Dialogue: 0,0:39:01.50,0:39:02.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么意思
Dialogue: 0,0:39:03.51,0:39:05.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们能留下了
Dialogue: 0,0:39:20.23,0:39:23.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,人类有了电力就会变得更危险
Dialogue: 0,0:39:23.73,0:39:25.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么要帮他们
Dialogue: 0,0:39:25.57,0:39:27.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他们似乎已经走投无路了
Dialogue: 0,0:39:28.45,0:39:31.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果赶走他们  以后一定会强攻过来
Dialogue: 0,0:39:31.45,0:39:33.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,来就来
Dialogue: 0,0:39:33.58,0:39:37.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,趁其疲弱  一举消灭他们
Dialogue: 0,0:39:38.04,0:39:41.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有多少猿类得为此牺牲
Dialogue: 0,0:39:43.55,0:39:46.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是一个缔造和平的机会
Dialogue: 0,0:39:47.22,0:39:50.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,让人类干完他们的活  他们就会离开
Dialogue: 0,0:39:52.43,0:39:54.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,人类干的活
Dialogue: 0,0:39:57.39,0:39:59.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,人类干的活
Dialogue: 0,0:40:02.11,0:40:04.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,人类干的活
Dialogue: 0,0:40:05.73,0:40:07.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,人类干的活
Dialogue: 0,0:40:45.61,0:40:47.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,科巴说
Dialogue: 0,0:40:47.28,0:40:49.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,猿族应该憎恨人类
Dialogue: 0,0:40:49.53,0:40:50.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,够了
Dialogue: 0,0:40:50.90,0:40:53.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,科巴在人类身上
Dialogue: 0,0:40:53.37,0:40:55.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只学到了仇恨
Dialogue: 0,0:41:09.58,0:41:12.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你得吃点东西
Dialogue: 0,0:41:12.84,0:41:14.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好  我只是
Dialogue: 0,0:41:14.97,0:41:17.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今天你的所作所为十分勇敢
Dialogue: 0,0:41:25.31,0:41:26.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,马尔科姆
Dialogue: 0,0:41:27.23,0:41:28.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道现在所有人都指望着你
Dialogue: 0,0:41:28.94,0:41:32.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我才不在乎  我一点也不在乎
Dialogue: 0,0:41:33.53,0:41:34.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我只在乎他
Dialogue: 0,0:41:36.78,0:41:38.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他经历的都不是小孩应该经历的事
Dialogue: 0,0:41:38.81,0:41:40.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不会让情况再次恶化了
Dialogue: 0,0:41:45.71,0:41:47.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道
Dialogue: 0,0:41:57.43,0:41:59.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也在试着消除和他的隔阂
Dialogue: 0,0:42:00.60,0:42:02.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但
Dialogue: 0,0:42:02.81,0:42:04.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,总有一天会的
Dialogue: 0,0:42:08.86,0:42:12.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,知道猿类可怕在哪儿吗
Dialogue: 0,0:42:12.07,0:42:15.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他们不需要电力  灯光
Dialogue: 0,0:42:16.28,0:42:19.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,暖气  什么都不需要
Dialogue: 0,0:42:19.20,0:42:20.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,伙计
Dialogue: 0,0:42:20.08,0:42:21.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是猿类的优势
Dialogue: 0,0:42:22.58,0:42:25.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是他们比人类强大的原因
Dialogue: 0,0:42:25.25,0:42:28.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,马尔科姆  今晚应该留一个人守夜
Dialogue: 0,0:42:28.09,0:42:30.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拿什么守  枪都被缴了
Dialogue: 0,0:42:30.34,0:42:31.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他们要真动了杀心  咱们根本活不到现在
Dialogue: 0,0:42:31.88,0:42:34.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他们可能只是不着急动手
Dialogue: 0,0:42:34.34,0:42:35.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,都已经干掉地球上一半的人了
Dialogue: 0,0:42:36.34,0:42:37.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拜托
Dialogue: 0,0:42:37.34,0:42:38.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么
Dialogue: 0,0:42:38.47,0:42:40.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这真不能怪猿类
Dialogue: 0,0:42:40.31,0:42:44.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那怪谁  本来就是猿流感
Dialogue: 0,0:42:44.10,0:42:45.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那也是实验室里科学家创造出来的病毒
Dialogue: 0,0:42:46.02,0:42:48.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,猩猩只是无辜的试验对象
Dialogue: 0,0:42:48.81,0:42:50.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别跟我扯大道理
Dialogue: 0,0:42:50.69,0:42:52.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你敢说你看到他们时
Dialogue: 0,0:42:52.38,0:42:53.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不觉得恶心吗
Dialogue: 0,0:42:58.03,0:42:59.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你以前不还有个女儿吗
Dialogue: 0,0:42:59.49,0:43:00.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,卡弗  够了
Dialogue: 0,0:43:00.53,0:43:02.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-她是怎么死的  -够了
Dialogue: 0,0:43:02.37,0:43:03.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你老婆也是
Dialogue: 0,0:43:03.41,0:43:06.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,卡弗  再不闭嘴我就要揍人了
Dialogue: 0,0:43:10.04,0:43:11.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:43:13.96,0:43:16.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,算我嘴贱
Dialogue: 0,0:43:21.31,0:43:23.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:43:41.99,0:43:46.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你听起来生病了  还好吗
Dialogue: 0,0:43:48.54,0:43:50.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只是需要休息
Dialogue: 0,0:43:57.34,0:44:00.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你操心人类的事就好
Dialogue: 0,0:45:01.11,0:45:02.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,科巴哪儿去了
Dialogue: 0,0:45:03.24,0:45:06.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,生闷气呢
Dialogue: 0,0:45:08.20,0:45:11.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他说要去打猎
Dialogue: 0,0:45:19.05,0:45:21.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看  下面有人类
Dialogue: 0,0:45:34.31,0:45:35.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们来这干什么
Dialogue: 0,0:45:36.52,0:45:39.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,凯撒相信人类
Dialogue: 0,0:45:39.74,0:45:41.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,科巴可不信
Dialogue: 0,0:45:43.36,0:45:45.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大多数武器应该还能用
Dialogue: 0,0:45:45.37,0:45:46.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:45:46.33,0:45:48.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们安排了人在那边试射
Dialogue: 0,0:46:37.92,0:46:39.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别动
Dialogue: 0,0:46:39.29,0:46:42.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,叫你别动  懂吗
Dialogue: 0,0:46:43.22,0:46:44.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,特里
Dialogue: 0,0:46:44.97,0:46:47.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,特里  快过来
Dialogue: 0,0:46:54.02,0:46:56.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我操
Dialogue: 0,0:46:58.77,0:47:01.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么办  怎么办
Dialogue: 0,0:47:01.86,0:47:03.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他从哪儿冒出来的
Dialogue: 0,0:47:04.03,0:47:06.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-要杀了他吗  -我也不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:47:10.45,0:47:13.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你还真他妈够丑的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:47:31.93,0:47:34.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,悠着点
Dialogue: 0,0:47:38.60,0:47:40.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想他应该是饿了
Dialogue: 0,0:47:40.27,0:47:42.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一定是和别的猿类走散了
Dialogue: 0,0:47:42.77,0:47:43.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你迷路了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:47:44.61,0:47:46.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要回家吗
Dialogue: 0,0:47:47.78,0:47:50.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,滚吧  离开这里  蠢猴子
Dialogue: 0,0:47:50.62,0:47:53.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快滚  照他说的做  快滚
Dialogue: 0,0:48:01.29,0:48:03.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那些枪足够杀死所有的猿类了
Dialogue: 0,0:48:04.63,0:48:06.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,必须警告凯撒
Dialogue: 0,0:48:06.22,0:48:08.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,天知道山上那些人在搞什么鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:48:28.15,0:48:30.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,堵住了  得炸开
Dialogue: 0,0:48:36.04,0:48:37.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不知道你曾有个女儿
Dialogue: 0,0:48:42.84,0:48:44.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:48:49.68,0:48:51.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她叫什么
Dialogue: 0,0:48:56.18,0:48:58.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,莎拉
Dialogue: 0,0:49:02.69,0:49:04.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我很遗憾
Dialogue: 0,0:49:11.15,0:49:15.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在有你和你父亲陪着我  所以
Dialogue: 0,0:49:22.25,0:49:24.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没错
Dialogue: 0,0:49:24.46,0:49:26.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-好了  -布置妥当了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:49:38.22,0:49:40.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,引线就那么长了
Dialogue: 0,0:49:40.81,0:49:43.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,注意安全
Dialogue: 0,0:49:44.15,0:49:48.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,三  二  一
Dialogue: 0,0:49:53.99,0:49:56.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-爸爸  -马尔科姆
Dialogue: 0,0:50:01.04,0:50:03.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,马尔科姆  马尔科姆
Dialogue: 0,0:50:03.83,0:50:04.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,爸爸
Dialogue: 0,0:50:05.42,0:50:06.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我看不到卡弗
Dialogue: 0,0:50:30.57,0:50:31.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,轻点
Dialogue: 0,0:50:31.90,0:50:33.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-扶好了  -好的
Dialogue: 0,0:50:36.32,0:50:38.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,骨头没断
Dialogue: 0,0:50:39.49,0:50:42.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,松开  好的
Dialogue: 0,0:50:54.26,0:50:55.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:50:57.30,0:50:58.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你救了我们的命
Dialogue: 0,0:50:59.43,0:51:00.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们得把那一大堆碎石给清理掉
Dialogue: 0,0:51:00.93,0:51:02.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可能会耽搁久一点
Dialogue: 0,0:51:02.14,0:51:03.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,多久
Dialogue: 0,0:51:42.26,0:51:43.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你好呀  小朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:51:52.36,0:51:54.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,干什么呢  弄好了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:51:57.45,0:51:58.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看什么看
Dialogue: 0,0:52:09.63,0:52:11.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,从箱子里滚出去
Dialogue: 0,0:52:16.88,0:52:19.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-老子杀了你  -卡弗  你干什么
Dialogue: 0,0:52:23.89,0:52:25.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要  不要
Dialogue: 0,0:52:25.31,0:52:27.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,凯撒  不
Dialogue: 0,0:52:27.18,0:52:28.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要
Dialogue: 0,0:52:42.91,0:52:47.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说过不准带枪
Dialogue: 0,0:52:51.08,0:52:52.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-不  别这样  -拜托
Dialogue: 0,0:53:24.45,0:53:26.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我并不知情
Dialogue: 0,0:53:33.33,0:53:36.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,人类  现在就走
Dialogue: 0,0:54:21.59,0:54:23.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这下完蛋了
Dialogue: 0,0:54:26.89,0:54:28.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,马尔科姆
Dialogue: 0,0:54:29.01,0:54:31.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,马尔科姆  你要去哪儿
Dialogue: 0,0:54:31.18,0:54:32.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,马尔科姆
Dialogue: 0,0:54:38.57,0:54:41.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拜托  拜托  我得和他谈谈
Dialogue: 0,0:54:44.07,0:54:47.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抱歉  都是我的错  我会让他离开的
Dialogue: 0,0:54:47.78,0:54:50.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是我的家
Dialogue: 0,0:54:52.29,0:54:54.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你不该上这来
Dialogue: 0,0:54:54.41,0:54:55.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道
Dialogue: 0,0:54:55.92,0:54:57.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,马尔科姆
Dialogue: 0,0:55:02.63,0:55:04.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她病了
Dialogue: 0,0:55:06.22,0:55:08.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她这样多久了
Dialogue: 0,0:55:15.98,0:55:18.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我带了药
Dialogue: 0,0:55:19.06,0:55:20.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抗生素
Dialogue: 0,0:55:23.24,0:55:24.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也许她能帮上忙
Dialogue: 0,0:55:26.91,0:55:30.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不信你
Dialogue: 0,0:55:32.91,0:55:34.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我能理解
Dialogue: 0,0:55:35.50,0:55:37.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但请相信我
Dialogue: 0,0:55:37.92,0:55:39.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们并不都像他那样
Dialogue: 0,0:55:39.75,0:55:44.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拜托  让我们帮你吧
Dialogue: 0,0:56:14.04,0:56:15.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一天
Dialogue: 0,0:56:17.50,0:56:20.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们只能待一天
Dialogue: 0,0:56:21.50,0:56:23.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,父亲  不行
Dialogue: 0,0:56:23.05,0:56:25.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-我们需要更多的时间  -就一天
Dialogue: 0,0:56:30.09,0:56:32.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,猿族会提供帮助
Dialogue: 0,0:56:35.85,0:56:38.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我才不帮忙呢
Dialogue: 0,0:56:42.19,0:56:44.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-你们疯了吧  -把他带走
Dialogue: 0,0:56:44.15,0:56:46.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,走  够了  过来  离开这里
Dialogue: 0,0:56:46.99,0:56:48.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,走吧  伙计
Dialogue: 0,0:56:54.83,0:56:56.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,行了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:56:57.58,0:56:59.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,给我过来
Dialogue: 0,0:57:04.50,0:57:06.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,上去
Dialogue: 0,0:57:21.02,0:57:23.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明天见  混蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:57:28.19,0:57:31.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,刚从城市回来  人类十分危险
Dialogue: 0,0:57:31.66,0:57:33.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,凯撒在哪儿
Dialogue: 0,0:57:37.37,0:57:40.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和人类在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:57:45.50,0:57:47.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,亚历克斯
Dialogue: 0,0:57:47.05,0:57:50.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个继电器坏了  另外找一个来
Dialogue: 0,0:57:50.30,0:57:51.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:58:12.78,0:58:14.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,凯撒
Dialogue: 0,0:58:24.21,0:58:25.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不  不  不  别
Dialogue: 0,0:58:25.88,0:58:27.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不  不  不
Dialogue: 0,0:58:34.51,0:58:38.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,凯撒在哪儿  我要见他
Dialogue: 0,0:58:38.35,0:58:40.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,凯撒
Dialogue: 0,0:58:56.32,0:59:00.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,人类攻击了你的子民
Dialogue: 0,0:59:00.66,0:59:04.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你还让他们留下
Dialogue: 0,0:59:06.50,0:59:09.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,置猿族于危险之中
Dialogue: 0,0:59:11.76,0:59:17.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,凯撒爱护人类却不顾猿族
Dialogue: 0,0:59:18.85,0:59:24.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不顾你的子民
Dialogue: 0,1:00:11.19,1:00:12.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,猿族
Dialogue: 0,1:00:13.65,1:00:15.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不
Dialogue: 0,1:00:15.49,1:00:17.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,杀
